ido" lang="io" hreflang="io" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ido</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-is"><a href="https://is.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — islandais" lang="is" hreflang="is" class="interlanguage-link-target">Íslenska</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-it"><a href="https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — italien" lang="it" hreflang="it" class="interlanguage-link-target">Italiano</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ja"><a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%B5%E3%83%B3%EF%BC%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3%E3%83%BB%E3%83%9A%E3%83%AB%E3%82%B9" title="サン＝ジョン・ペルス — japonais" lang="ja" hreflang="ja" class="interlanguage-link-target">日本語</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-jv"><a href="https://jv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — javanais" lang="jv" hreflang="jv" class="interlanguage-link-target">Jawa</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ka"><a href="https://ka.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E1%83%A1%E1%83%94%E1%83%9C-%E1%83%9F%E1%83%9D%E1%83%9C_%E1%83%9E%E1%83%94%E1%83%A0%E1%83%A1%E1%83%98" title="სენ-ჟონ პერსი — géorgien" lang="ka" hreflang="ka" class="interlanguage-link-target">ქართული</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kk"><a href="https://kk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BD-%D0%96%D0%BE%D0%BD_%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%81" title="Сен-Жон Перс — kazakh" lang="kk" hreflang="kk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Қазақша</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kn"><a href="https://kn.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%B2%B8%E0%B3%88%E0%B2%82%E0%B2%9F%E0%B3%8D-_%E0%B2%9C%E0%B2%BE%E0%B2%A8%E0%B3%8D_%E0%B2%AA%E0%B2%B0%E0%B3%8D%E0%B2%B8%E0%B3%86" title="ಸೈಂಟ್- ಜಾನ್ ಪರ್ಸೆ — kannada" lang="kn" hreflang="kn" class="interlanguage-link-target">ಕನ್ನಡ</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ko"><a href="https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%83%9D%EC%A1%B4_%ED%8E%98%EB%A5%B4%EC%8A%A4" title="생존 페르스 — coréen" lang="ko" hreflang="ko" class="interlanguage-link-target">한국어</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ku"><a href="https://ku.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — kurde" lang="ku" hreflang="ku" class="interlanguage-link-target">Kurdî</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-la"><a href="https://la.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — latin" lang="la" hreflang="la" class="interlanguage-link-target">Latina</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-lb"><a href="https://lb.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — luxembourgeois" lang="lb" hreflang="lb" class="interlanguage-link-target">Lëtzebuergesch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-lv"><a href="https://lv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sen%C5%BEons_P%C4%93rss" title="Senžons Pērss — letton" lang="lv" hreflang="lv" class="interlanguage-link-target">Latviešu</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-mk"><a href="https://mk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BD-%D0%8F%D0%BE%D0%BD_%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%81" title="Сен-Џон Перс — macédonien" lang="mk" hreflang="mk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Македонски</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-mr"><a href="https://mr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%9F-%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%89%E0%A4%A8_%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B8" title="सेंट-जॉन पर्स — marathi" lang="mr" hreflang="mr" class="interlanguage-link-target">मराठी</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ms"><a href="https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — malais" lang="ms" hreflang="ms" class="interlanguage-link-target">Bahasa Melayu</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl"><a href="https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Perse" title="Saint-John Perse — néerlandais" lang="nl" hreflang="nl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Nederlands</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nn"><a href="https://nn.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-John_Pe