<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-9"><a href="#Liste_des_œuvres"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Liste des œuvres</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-10"><a href="#Cycle_antillais"><span class="tocnumber">4.1</span> <span class="toctext">Cycle antillais</span></a></li>
