<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Correspondance">Correspondance</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Saint-John_Perse&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=16" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Correspondance">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Saint-John_Perse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Modifier la section : Correspondance">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
